<body class = "bg">	
	<!-- 2 Panel Style. Left is Title, classifications and right is description-->
	<div class = "allWrap">
		<div class = "row">
			<div class ="bigTitle">ThoughtSpot Allegro</div>
		</div>
		<div class = "row">
			<div class ="subBigTitle">An intimate companion for your mental health needs</div>
		</div>
		<div class = "row">
			<!-- Description section -->
			<div class = "col-md-6">
				<div class = "descriptionContainer">
					<div class = "row">
						<div class="descSubtitle">What it is</div>
						<div class="descElab">
							<p>
								Thoughtspot Allegro is an Android companion app that is designed to give users immediately relevant venues that can improve their mental health. Whether users feel uplifted, stressed or even sexually frustrated, they can easily transition to their desired venue category and find the places closest to them. 
							</p>
							<p>
								We allow users to be vocal about the places they've been to upvote places for their helpfulness or even suggest new places using the Google Maps API. 
							</p>
							<p>
								Going beyond suggestion, we created an environment for users to anonymously divulge their troubles in an "instant help room", where they can find and obtain advice from peers and dedicated mental specialists.  
							</p>
							<p>
														
							</p>
						</div>

						<div class="descSubtitle">Motivation</div>
						<div class="descElab">
							<p>
								Mental health is often a touchy topic, but there is a necessity to tackle issues head on. One way is by making locations that can improve one's mentality clear. 
							</p>
							<p>
								Finding and displaying locations is rarely enough however, which paved way to the idea of an instant help room, where users can easily find someone willing to help them. 
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="descSubtitle">Source Code</div>
						<div class="descElab">
							You can check out the source code <a href="https://github.com/marcokstephen/ThoughtSpotAllegro">here</a>!<br>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<!-- Title, brief, photo section -->
			<div class = "col-md-6">
				<div class = "row">
					<div class = "mediaContainer">
						<div id="carousel-example-generic" class="carousel slide" data-ride="false" data-interval="false">
						  	<!-- Indicators -->
						  	<ol class="carousel-indicators">
						    	<li data-target="#carousel-example-generic" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
						    	<li data-target="#carousel-example-generic" data-slide-to="1"></li>
						    	<li data-target="#carousel-example-generic" data-slide-to="2"></li>
							  </ol>

						  	<!-- Wrapper for slides -->
						  	<div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
						    	<div class="item active">
					      			<%= image_tag("placeholder2.jpg", :alt => "placeholder", :class => "carouImage") %>
						    	</div>
						    	<div class="item">
						      		<%= image_tag("placeholder2.jpg", :alt => "placeholder", :class => "carouImage") %>
						    	</div>
						    	<div class="item">
						      		<%= image_tag("placeholder2.jpg", :alt => "placeholder", :class => "carouImage") %>
						    	</div>
						    	
							</div>

						  	<!-- Controls -->
						  	<a class="left carousel-control" href="#carousel-example-generic" role="button" data-slide="prev">
						    	<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></span>
						    	<span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
						  	</a>
							<a class="right carousel-control" href="#carousel-example-generic" role="button" data-slide="next">
						    	<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span>
						    	<span class="sr-only">Next</span>
							</a>
						</div>
						<!-- <div class = "row"> -->
							<!-- <div class ="carouselContainer"> -->
								
							<!-- </div> -->
						<!-- </div> -->
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class = "row">
					<div class = "bulletContainer">
						<div class = "row">
							<div class = "col-md-3 text-center left_img">
								<div class = "ci_cont">
									<%=image_tag("when_icon.png", :alt => "placeholder", :class => "circle_icon")%>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class = "col-md-9 right_descrip">
								<div class ="iconBriefContainer">
									<%=image_tag("hackathought_banner.jpg", :alt => "Sportshack14 logo", :class => "event_banner")%>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class = "row">
							<div class = "col-md-3 text-center left_img">
								<div class = "ci_cont">
									<%=image_tag("materials_icon.png", :alt => "placeholder", :class => "circle_icon")%>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class = "col-md-9 right_descrip">
								<div class ="iconBriefContainer">
									<p>Android Device</p>
									<p>Android Studio, Thoughtspot Database, Google App Engine</p>
									<p>Java, mySQL, Python</p>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class = "row">
							<div class = "col-md-3 text-center left_img">
								<div class = "ci_cont">
									<%=image_tag("teammates_icon.png", :alt => "placeholder", :class => "circle_icon")%>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class = "col-md-9 right_descrip">
								<div class ="iconBriefContainer">
									<ul class = "team_members">
										<li class = "team_members">Kevin Zhu</li>
										<li class = "team_members">Ken Liao</li>
										<li class = "team_members">Stephen Marcok</li>
										<li class = "team_members">Carlos Lau</li>
									</ul>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</body>


